/* Editor — Environment */
"Plain `KEY=VALUE` pairs exported into every shell in the VM via `proxy.env` (sourced from `.bashrc`). No proxy substitution — values land on the VM verbatim, so don't put secrets here. Good for log levels, feature flags, build toggles." = "通过 `proxy.env`（由 `.bashrc` 加载）导出到虚拟机内每个 shell 的简单 `KEY=VALUE` 键值对。不会被代理替换 —— 值会原样到达虚拟机，因此请不要在此放入机密。适合日志级别、功能开关、构建开关等。";
