/* Compromise detection — alert + wipe-on-launch flow */
"⛔ VM “%@” has been compromised" = "⛔ 虚拟机“%@”已被入侵";
"Bromure detected an outbound attempt to leak a session credential to a host it was not minted for. The VM has been paused." = "Bromure 检测到向非授权主机外发会话凭据的尝试。虚拟机已暂停。";
"Detected leaks:" = "检测到的泄露:";
"  • %1$@ (%2$@) — expected %3$@, sent to %4$@\n" = "  • %1$@(%2$@)— 应为 %3$@,发送至 %4$@\n";
"Save for Investigation lets you pick a folder where Bromure will copy the disk image and gzipped archives of the home directory and shared folders. The VM's RAM state is discarded. The VM is then shut down and the profile is marked compromised." = "“保存以供调查”允许您选择一个文件夹,Bromure 会将磁盘映像、主目录和共享文件夹的 gzip 归档复制到其中。虚拟机的内存状态将被丢弃。随后虚拟机会关机,该配置文件将被标记为已入侵。";
"Save for Investigation" = "保存以供调查";
"Continue" = "继续";
"Save Investigation Here" = "在此保存调查内容";
"Choose a folder to receive the disk image, home archive, and shared-folder archives for “%@”." = "请选择一个文件夹用于保存“%@”的磁盘映像、主目录归档以及共享文件夹归档。";
"⛔ “%@” is marked as compromised" = "⛔ “%@”已被标记为已入侵";
"Bromure refused to boot this VM because the proxy detected an outbound credential leak in a previous session." = "Bromure 拒绝启动此虚拟机,因为代理在之前的会话中检测到了外发凭据泄露。";
"To continue, the VM disk image and the persistent home folder must be wiped. Your tokens, ssh keys, and profile settings are preserved." = "若要继续,必须清除虚拟机的磁盘映像和持久化的主目录。您的令牌、SSH 密钥和配置文件设置将保留。";
"WARNING: shared folders are NOT wiped. Compromised packages or files may still be present in:" = "警告:共享文件夹不会被清除。被入侵的软件包或文件可能仍存在于:";
"Inspect those folders before launching anything that re-uses them." = "在启动任何重用这些文件夹的程序之前,请先检查它们。";
"Wipe and Launch" = "清除并启动";
"Compromised — launching will prompt to wipe disk and home" = "已入侵 — 启动时会提示清除磁盘和主目录";
